{"tid":1046423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京一年「拾金不昧」現金額超過38億日元（2.7億港元）","createTime":"2019-03-04T08:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T09:50:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b66d8e6c376372e0ca631eba36d3d44ceb21101","tid":1046423,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"東京警視廳失物招領中心的統計顯示，在2018年一年時間內，被上交至東京都內派出所及警察署等的遺失現金比上年增加2.4％，增至約38.4億日元（約合港元2.7億），刷新了歷史最高紀錄。這一金額已連續3年創新高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據失物招領中心介紹，2018年1年內交還給失主的現金約為28.2億日元。此外，約5億日元被交給拾到者，另有失主不明且拾到者放棄所有權的約5.6億日元成為東京都的收入。從高額拾金不昧的例子來看，曾有人在一座建築物的拆除現場拾到約2540萬日元（約合人民幣152萬元），並上交警方。<br />\n<br />\n       警視廳受理的失物總數約為414萬件（比上年增加4.6%），達到歷史最多。從遺失物品類別來看，工作證及保險證等「證明類」最多，約為75.2萬張，其次是IC乘車卡等「有價證券類」和「衣服鞋子類」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/34548-2019-03-04-10-09-36.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Fpoliticsaeconomy%2Fpoliticsasociety%2F34548-2019-03-04-10-09-36.html&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4DKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=24f55eca\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/34548-2019-03-04-10-09-36.html</a>"},{"pid":"bbbc921411c0e43b0aa01ea0129419225f39dc1a","tid":1046423,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"衫褲鞋襪都計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成地精"},{"pid":"f21190b8e0ebe8d9b02759a3b9598cb7196ee192","tid":1046423,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d79a3f8786b837939981b49d465b892efb3482","tid":1046423,"uid":30309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"上年係淺早唔見card holder<br />\n第二日有得警視廳拎番<i